    'description' => 'Solve an ASCII maze using BFS (breadth-first search). Takes a maze string (like maze_generator output) with \'#\', \' \', \'S\', \'E\' characters. Returns the shortest solution path as coordinates, path length, and a marked-up solution grid. Also supports wall char and path char customization. Pure function, no side effects.',
